text: Heliophanus maluti is a species of jumping spiders in the genus Heliophanus that lives in Lesotho. It was first identified in 2014. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Fauna of Lesotho Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Spiders described in 2014 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
